(4, NULL, NULL, 'cookie.data', '{\"short_desc\":\"We may use cookies or any other tracking technologies when you visit our website, including any other media form, mobile website, or mobile application related or connected to help customize the Site and improve your experience.\",\"description\":\"<h1 style=\\\"text-align: justify; \\\"><b><font color=\\\"#000000\\\" face=\\\"helvetica\\\">Cookie Policy of Multitech<\\/font><\\/b><\\/h1><div style=\\\"text-align: justify; \\\"><b><font color=\\\"#000000\\\" face=\\\"helvetica\\\"><br><\\/font><\\/b><\\/div><div style=\\\"text-align: justify; \\\"><b><font color=\\\"#000000\\\" face=\\\"helvetica\\\"><br><\\/font><\\/b><\\/div><div style=\\\"text-align: justify; \\\"><font color=\\\"#000000\\\" face=\\\"helvetica\\\"><br><\\/font><\\/div><div><div style=\\\"text-align: justify; \\\"><font color=\\\"#000000\\\" face=\\\"helvetica\\\" size=\\\"4\\\">Welcome to Multitech. This Cookie Policy is designed to help you understand how and why&nbsp;cookies are used on our website. At Multitech, we\\u2019re committed to providing a safe, user-friendly, and personalized shopping experience. To achieve this, we use cookies and similar&nbsp;technologies.&nbsp;This policy explains what cookies are, how we use them, and how they help us serve you better.&nbsp;Whether you\\u2019re browsing through CCTV cameras, network switches, or the latest computer&nbsp;gadgets, our goal is to make sure your experience is smooth, secure, and enjoyable.&nbsp;By continuing to use our website, you agree to our use of cookies as described in this policy.<\\/font><\\/div><div style=\\\"text-align: justify; \\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 1rem;\\\"><font color=\\\"#000000\\\" face=\\\"helvetica\\\"><br><\\/font><\\/span><\\/div><h2 style=\\\"text-align: justify; \\\"><b><font color=\\\"#000000\\\" face=\\\"helvetica\\\">What Are Cookies?<\\/font><\\/b><\\/h2><div style=\\\"text-align: justify; \\\"><font color=\\\"#000000\\\" face=\\\"helvetica\\\"><br><\\/font><\\/div><div style=\\\"text-align: justify; \\\"><font color=\\\"#000000\\\" face=\\\"helvetica\\\" size=\\\"4\\\">Cookies are small text files that websites store on your device when you visit them. These files&nbsp;contain a small amount of data that helps websites remember your actions, preferences, and&nbsp;behavior over time. When you visit our website again, your browser sends the cookie back to our&nbsp;server, allowing the site to recognize you and provide a more tailored experience.&nbsp;Cookies are widely used across the internet and are essential for websites to function properly.&nbsp;They help us remember things like your login information, what\\u2019s in your cart, which pages you&nbsp;visited, and more. Without cookies, using an online store would be much less convenient.&nbsp;Cookies do not harm your device and do not access any data or files from your computer, tablet,&nbsp;or smartphone. They simply store information to improve your visit.<\\/font><\\/div><h2 style=\\\"\\\"><div style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 16px;\\\"><b><font color=\\\"#000000\\\" face=\\\"helvetica\\\"><br><\\/font><\\/b><\\/span><\\/div><div style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><b style=\\\"font-size: 2rem;\\\"><font color=\\\"#000000\\\" face=\\\"helvetica\\\">Why Cookies Are Important for Your Experience?<\\/font><\\/b><\\/div><\\/h2><div style=\\\"text-align: justify; \\\"><font color=\\\"#000000\\\" face=\\\"helvetica\\\" size=\\\"4\\\"><br><\\/font><\\/div><div style=\\\"text-align: justify; \\\"><font color=\\\"#000000\\\" face=\\\"helvetica\\\" size=\\\"4\\\">When you visit Multitech, we want everything to work seamlessly. Whether you\\u2019re comparing&nbsp;CCTV models, checking out the latest Wi-Fi routers, or placing an order for a gaming keyboard,&nbsp;cookies help us remember your preferences and ensure the website loads quickly and works&nbsp;correctly.&nbsp;<\\/font><\\/div><div style=\\\"text-align: justify; \\\"><b><font color=\\\"#000000\\\" face=\\\"helvetica\\\" size=\\\"4\\\">For example:&nbsp;<\\/font><\\/b><\\/div><div style=\\\"text-align: justify; \\\"><font color=\\\"#000000\\\" face=\\\"helvetica\\\" size=\\\"4\\\">When you log into your account, a cookie keeps you logged in during your session.&nbsp;When you add items to your shopping cart and return later, cookies help us remember your&nbsp;selections.&nbsp;When we analyze which product pages are popular, cookies give us valuable insights into what&nbsp;you like, so we can improve.&nbsp;In short, cookies allow us to offer you a faster, smarter, and more personalized experience every&nbsp;time you visit our website.<\\/font><\\/div><div style=\\\"text-align: justify; \\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 1rem;\\\"><font color=\\\"#000000\\\" face=\\\"helvetica\\\"><br><\\/font><\\/span><\\/div><h2 style=\\\"text-align: justify; \\\"><b><font color=\\\"#000000\\\" face=\\\"helvetica\\\">How We Use Cookies at Multitech?<\\/font><\\/b><\\/h2><div style=\\\"text-align: justify; \\\"><font color=\\\"#000000\\\" face=\\\"helvetica\\\"><br><\\/font><\\/div><div style=\\\"text-align: justify; \\\"><font color=\\\"#000000\\\" face=\\\"helvetica\\\" size=\\\"4\\\">At Multitech, we use cookies in several ways that benefit both you and our business. Here\\u2019s how:&nbsp;<\\/font><\\/div><div style=\\\"text-align: justify; \\\"><b><font color=\\\"#000000\\\" face=\\\"helvetica\\\" size=\\\"4\\\">1. To Provide a Personalized Experience&nbsp;<\\/font><\\/b><\\/div><div style=\\\"text-align: justify; \\\"><font color=\\\"#000000\\\" face=\\\"helvetica\\\" size=\\\"4\\\">We believe in making your visit feel personal. Cookies allow us to remember your actions and&nbsp;preferences so you don\\u2019t need to set them each time you come back. This means we can show&nbsp;you products that match your interests, keep your shopping cart saved, and offer content based&nbsp;on your previous visits.&nbsp;<\\/font><\\/div><div style=\\\"text-align: justify; \\\"><b><font color=\\\"#000000\\\" face=\\\"helvetica\\\" size=\\\"4\\\">2. To Understand Visitor Behavior&nbsp;<\\/font><\\/b><\\/div><div style=\\\"text-align: justify; \\\"><font color=\\\"#000000\\\" face=\\\"helvetica\\\" size=\\\"4\\\">We want to know what\\u2019s working well on our website and what\\u2019s not. Cookies help us track how&nbsp;people use our website. For example, we can see how many users visit a certain page, how long&nbsp;they stay, and which links they click. This information helps us improve the design, content, and&nbsp;navigation of our website to serve you better.&nbsp;<\\/font><\\/div><div style=\\\"text-align: justify; \\\"><b><font color=\\\"#000000\\\" face=\\\"helvetica\\\" size=\\\"4\\\">3. To Improve Site Performance&nbsp;<\\/font><\\/b><\\/div><div style=\\\"text-align: justify; \\\"><font color=\\\"#000000\\\" face=\\\"helvetica\\\" size=\\\"4\\\">Speed matters. Cookies help us measure the load time of different pages, identify any technical&nbsp;issues, and make the site faster and more responsive. If something\\u2019s not working, cookies help&nbsp;us figure out what went wrong so we can fix it quickly.&nbsp;<\\/font><\\/div><div style=\\\"text-align: justify; \\\"><b><font color=\\\"#000000\\\" face=\\\"helvetica\\\" size=\\\"4\\\">4. To Help With Marketing and Promotions&nbsp;<\\/font><\\/b><\\/div><div style=\\\"text-align: justify; \\\"><font color=\\\"#000000\\\" face=\\\"helvetica\\\" size=\\\"4\\\">Cookies help us deliver relevant promotions and ads. For instance, if you\\u2019ve shown interest in&nbsp;surveillance equipment, we can highlight related deals or products that might interest you. We&nbsp;also use cookies to see how our ads are performing and which campaigns are bringing in traffic.&nbsp;<\\/font><\\/div><div style=\\\"text-align: justify; \\\"><b><font color=\\\"#000000\\\" face=\\\"helvetica\\\" size=\\\"4\\\">5. To Keep Your Account and Data Safe&nbsp;<\\/font><\\/b><\\/div><div style=\\\"text-align: justify; \\\"><font color=\\\"#000000\\\" face=\\\"helvetica\\\" size=\\\"4\\\">Security is our top priority. Cookies help us detect unusual or suspicious activity. They alert us to&nbsp;anything that might indicate a security risk, such as repeated failed login attempts. This helps us&nbsp;protect your data and our website from threats.<\\/font><\\/div><div style=\\\"text-align: justify; \\\"><font color=\\\"#000000\\\" face=\\\"helvetica\\\"><br><\\/font><\\/div><h2 style=\\\"text-align: justify; \\\"><b><font color=\\\"#000000\\\" face=\\\"helvetica\\\">Our Commitment to Transparency<\\/font><\\/b><\\/h2><div style=\\\"text-align: justify; \\\"><font color=\\\"#000000\\\" face=\\\"helvetica\\\"><br><\\/font><\\/div><div style=\\\"text-align: justify; \\\"><font color=\\\"#000000\\\" face=\\\"helvetica\\\" size=\\\"4\\\">At Multitech, we believe in transparency. We want you to feel confident and informed every time&nbsp;you visit our site. That\\u2019s why we\\u2019re upfront about how we use cookies.&nbsp;We never use cookies to collect sensitive personal information like passwords or payment details.&nbsp;All the data we collect through cookies is anonymous or aggregated. It is used strictly to improve&nbsp;our services and tailor your experience.&nbsp;We also work with trusted third-party services (like analytics or advertising tools) that may place&nbsp;their own cookies when you visit our site. These cookies help us gain deeper insights into how&nbsp;people use our site or allow us to reach you with relevant information. We make sure our&nbsp;partners follow strict data protection and privacy standards.<\\/font><\\/div><h2 style=\\\"\\\"><div style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 16px;\\\"><b><font color=\\\"#000000\\\" face=\\\"helvetica\\\"><br><\\/font><\\/b><\\/span><\\/div><div style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><b style=\\\"font-size: 2rem;\\\"><font color=\\\"#000000\\\" face=\\\"helvetica\\\">How Long Do Cookies Stay on Your Device?<\\/font><\\/b><\\/div><\\/h2><div style=\\\"text-align: justify; \\\"><font color=\\\"#000000\\\" face=\\\"helvetica\\\"><br><\\/font><\\/div><div style=\\\"text-align: justify; \\\"><font color=\\\"#000000\\\" face=\\\"helvetica\\\" size=\\\"4\\\">Some cookies are temporary. They only last while you\\u2019re browsing and disappear when you close&nbsp;your browser. These are often called session cookies.&nbsp;Other cookies are more permanent. They stay on your device for a set period, even after you\\u2019ve&nbsp;left our website. These are known as persistent cookies and help us remember your settings and&nbsp;preferences for your next visit.&nbsp;The length of time a cookie stays on your device depends on its purpose. Some may last a few&nbsp;hours; others may remain for weeks or months. You can delete them at any time through your&nbsp;browser settings.<\\/font><\\/div><div style=\\\"text-align: justify; \\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 1rem;\\\"><font color=\\\"#000000\\\" face=\\\"helvetica\\\"><br><\\/font><\\/span><\\/div><h2 style=\\\"text-align: justify; \\\"><b><font color=\\\"#000000\\\" face=\\\"helvetica\\\">Your Control Over Cookies<\\/font><\\/b><\\/h2><div style=\\\"text-align: justify; \\\"><font color=\\\"#000000\\\" face=\\\"helvetica\\\"><br><\\/font><\\/div><div style=\\\"text-align: justify; \\\"><font color=\\\"#000000\\\" face=\\\"helvetica\\\" size=\\\"4\\\">We fully respect your choices when it comes to how your personal data is handled. You have the&nbsp;ability to review, manage, or remove cookies anytime through the settings in your web browser.&nbsp;Here\\u2019s how:&nbsp;<\\/font><\\/div><div style=\\\"text-align: justify; \\\"><font color=\\\"#000000\\\" face=\\\"helvetica\\\" size=\\\"4\\\"><b>Delete existing cookies:<\\/b> You can delete all cookies stored on your device through your browser\\u2019s&nbsp;privacy settings.&nbsp;<\\/font><\\/div><div style=\\\"text-align: justify; \\\"><font color=\\\"#000000\\\" face=\\\"helvetica\\\" size=\\\"4\\\"><b>Block new cookies:<\\/b> You can choose to block cookies altogether or only from specific websites.&nbsp;<\\/font><\\/div><div style=\\\"text-align: justify; \\\"><font color=\\\"#000000\\\" face=\\\"helvetica\\\" size=\\\"4\\\"><b>Set alerts<\\/b>: Some browsers allow you to receive a notification every time a cookie is used.<\\/font><\\/div><div style=\\\"text-align: justify; \\\"><font color=\\\"#000000\\\" face=\\\"helvetica\\\" size=\\\"4\\\"><br><\\/font><\\/div><div style=\\\"text-align: justify; \\\"><font color=\\\"#000000\\\" face=\\\"helvetica\\\" size=\\\"4\\\">Please note, if you disable cookies, some parts of our website may not work as intended. For&nbsp;example, you may not be able to log in, add items to your cart, or complete a purchase. To enjoy&nbsp;the smoothest and most personalized browsing experience, we suggest keeping cookies enabled.<\\/font><\\/div><div style=\\\"text-align: justify; \\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 1rem;\\\"><font color=\\\"#000000\\\" face=\\\"helvetica\\\"><br><\\/font><\\/span><\\/div><h2 style=\\\"text-align: justify; \\\"><b><font color=\\\"#000000\\\" face=\\\"helvetica\\\">How to Manage Cookies in Different Browsers?<\\/font><\\/b><\\/h2><div style=\\\"text-align: justify; \\\"><font color=\\\"#000000\\\" face=\\\"helvetica\\\"><br><\\/font><\\/div><div style=\\\"text-align: justify; \\\"><font color=\\\"#000000\\\" face=\\\"helvetica\\\" size=\\\"4\\\">If you\\u2019re unsure how to control cookies, here are links to guides for popular browsers:&nbsp;<\\/font><\\/div><div style=\\\"text-align: justify; \\\"><font color=\\\"#000000\\\" face=\\\"helvetica\\\" size=\\\"4\\\">Google Chrome: chrome:\\/\\/settings\\/cookies&nbsp;<\\/font><\\/div><div style=\\\"text-align: justify; \\\"><font color=\\\"#000000\\\" face=\\\"helvetica\\\" size=\\\"4\\\">Microsoft Edge: edge:\\/\\/settings\\/privacy&nbsp;<\\/font><\\/div><div style=\\\"text-align: justify; \\\"><font color=\\\"#000000\\\" face=\\\"helvetica\\\" size=\\\"4\\\">Safari: Go to Safari &gt; Preferences &gt; Privacy&nbsp;<\\/font><\\/div><div style=\\\"text-align: justify; \\\"><font color=\\\"#000000\\\" face=\\\"helvetica\\\" size=\\\"4\\\">You can also use third-party browser extensions or plugins to manage cookies more precisely.<\\/font><\\/div><div style=\\\"text-align: justify; \\\"><font color=\\\"#000000\\\" face=\\\"helvetica\\\"><br><\\/font><\\/div><h2 style=\\\"text-align: justify; \\\"><b><font color=\\\"#000000\\\" face=\\\"helvetica\\\">Cookies and Third-Party Services<\\/font><\\/b><\\/h2><div style=\\\"text-align: justify; \\\"><font color=\\\"#000000\\\" face=\\\"helvetica\\\"><br><\\/font><\\/div><div style=\\\"text-align: justify; \\\"><font color=\\\"#000000\\\" face=\\\"helvetica\\\" size=\\\"4\\\">Sometimes we use third-party services to improve our website and marketing. These services&nbsp;may set their own cookies when you visit our site. For example, we use tools like:&nbsp;<\\/font><\\/div><div style=\\\"text-align: justify; \\\"><font color=\\\"#000000\\\" face=\\\"helvetica\\\" size=\\\"4\\\">Google Analytics \\u2013 To understand how users interact with our website.&nbsp;<\\/font><\\/div><div style=\\\"text-align: justify; \\\"><font color=\\\"#000000\\\" face=\\\"helvetica\\\" size=\\\"4\\\">Facebook Pixel \\u2013 To help us deliver more relevant ads on Facebook.&nbsp;<\\/font><\\/div><div style=\\\"text-align: justify; \\\"><font color=\\\"#000000\\\" face=\\\"helvetica\\\" size=\\\"4\\\">Live chat tools \\u2013 To offer real-time support and communication.&nbsp;<\\/font><\\/div><div style=\\\"text-align: justify; \\\"><font color=\\\"#000000\\\" face=\\\"helvetica\\\" size=\\\"4\\\">These third parties may collect and process data in accordance with their own privacy and cookie&nbsp;policies. We recommend reviewing their policies if you want to understand how your data is used&nbsp;beyond our website.<\\/font><\\/div><div style=\\\"text-align: justify; \\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 1rem;\\\"><font color=\\\"#000000\\\" face=\\\"helvetica\\\"><br><\\/font><\\/span><\\/div><h2 style=\\\"text-align: justify; \\\"><b><font color=\\\"#000000\\\" face=\\\"helvetica\\\">Updates to This Cookie Policy<\\/font><\\/b><\\/h2><div style=\\\"text-align: justify; \\\"><font color=\\\"#000000\\\" face=\\\"helvetica\\\"><br><\\/font><\\/div><div style=\\\"text-align: justify; \\\"><font color=\\\"#000000\\\" face=\\\"helvetica\\\" size=\\\"4\\\">We may update this Cookie Policy from time to time as our website evolves, technologies change,&nbsp;or legal requirements are updated. When we make changes, we\\u2019ll update the \\u201cLast Updated\\u201d&nbsp;date at the bottom of this page. We encourage you to check this policy occasionally to stay&nbsp;informed.&nbsp;By continuing to use our site after any updates to this policy, you agree to the latest terms and&nbsp;practices described here. If we make major changes, we may notify you by email or a message&nbsp;on the website.<\\/font><\\/div><div style=\\\"text-align: justify; \\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 1rem;\\\"><font color=\\\"#000000\\\" face=\\\"helvetica\\\"><br><\\/font><\\/span><\\/div><h2 style=\\\"text-align: justify; \\\"><b><font color=\\\"#000000\\\" face=\\\"helvetica\\\">Your Privacy Matters<\\/font><\\/b><\\/h2><div style=\\\"text-align: justify; \\\"><font color=\\\"#000000\\\" face=\\\"helvetica\\\"><br><\\/font><\\/div><div style=\\\"text-align: justify; \\\"><font color=\\\"#000000\\\" face=\\\"helvetica\\\" size=\\\"4\\\">At Multitech, we value your privacy as much as your experience. Cookies help us serve you better&nbsp;without ever compromising your personal information. Our mission is to provide top-quality tech&nbsp;products\\u2014from surveillance cameras to networking gear\\u2014with honesty, care, and clarity.&nbsp;If you ever have questions about how we use cookies or how we protect your data, we\\u2019re here&nbsp;to help.<\\/font><\\/div><div style=\\\"text-align: justify; \\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 1rem;\\\"><font color=\\\"#000000\\\" face=\\\"helvetica\\\"><br><\\/font><\\/span><\\/div><div style=\\\"text-align: justify; \\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 1rem;\\\"><font color=\\\"#000000\\\" face=\\\"helvetica\\\"><br><\\/font><\\/span><\\/div><div style=\\\"\\\"><hr style=\\\"text-align: justify; \\\"><\\/div><div style=\\\"text-align: justify; \\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 1rem;\\\"><font color=\\\"#000000\\\" face=\\\"helvetica\\\"><br><\\/font><\\/span><\\/div><div style=\\\"text-align: justify; \\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 1rem;\\\"><font color=\\\"#000000\\\" face=\\\"helvetica\\\">&nbsp;<\\/font><\\/span><\\/div><h2 style=\\\"text-align: justify; \\\"><b><font color=\\\"#000000\\\" face=\\\"helvetica\\\">Where can I get further information?&nbsp;<\\/font><\\/b><\\/h2><div style=\\\"text-align: justify; \\\"><font color=\\\"#000000\\\" face=\\\"helvetica\\\"><br><\\/font><\\/div><div style=\\\"text-align: justify; \\\"><font color=\\\"#000000\\\" face=\\\"helvetica\\\">If you have any questions or concerns about our use of cookies or other technologies, please&nbsp;<span style=\\\"font-size: 1rem;\\\">contact us at support@multitech.com.bd or by post at:&nbsp;<\\/span><\\/font><\\/div><div style=\\\"text-align: justify; \\\"><font size=\\\"5\\\" color=\\\"#000000\\\" face=\\\"helvetica\\\"><b>Head Office&nbsp;<\\/b>&nbsp;<\\/font><\\/div><div style=\\\"text-align: justify; \\\"><font size=\\\"4\\\" color=\\\"#000000\\\" face=\\\"helvetica\\\"><b>Multitech&nbsp;&nbsp;<\\/b><\\/font><\\/div><div style=\\\"text-align: justify; \\\"><font size=\\\"4\\\" color=\\\"#000000\\\" face=\\\"helvetica\\\">51, Kazi Villa, 3rd Floor, Suvastu Arcade ICT Bhaban Goli, New Elephant Road, Dhaka-1205,&nbsp;<\\/font><\\/div><div style=\\\"text-align: justify; \\\"><font size=\\\"4\\\" color=\\\"#000000\\\" face=\\\"helvetica\\\">Bangladesh.&nbsp;<\\/font><\\/div><div style=\\\"text-align: justify; \\\"><font size=\\\"4\\\" color=\\\"#000000\\\" face=\\\"helvetica\\\">Email: <\\/font><font size=\\\"4\\\" face=\\\"helvetica\\\" color=\\\"#0033cc\\\">support@multitech.com.bd&nbsp;&nbsp;<\\/font><\\/div><div style=\\\"text-align: justify; \\\"><font size=\\\"4\\\" color=\\\"#000000\\\" face=\\\"helvetica\\\">Contact: +880 1894-683430&nbsp;<\\/font><\\/div><\\/div>\",\"status\":1}', NULL, '2020-07-04 23:42:52', '2025-08-02 19:40:45'),
(5, 'basic', 'privacy-policy', 'policy_pages.element', '{\"title\":\"Privacy Policy\",\"details\":\"<div class=\\\"mb-5\\\" style=\\\"margin-bottom:3rem;\\\"><h1 style=\\\"text-align:justify;line-height:1.3;\\\"><b><font color=\\\"#000000\\\" face=\\\"helvetica\\\">Privacy Policy of Multitech<\\/font><\\/b><\\/h1><div><hr style=\\\"text-align:justify;\\\" \\/><\\/div><div style=\\\"text-align:justify;\\\"><b><font color=\\\"#000000\\\" face=\\\"helvetica\\\"><br \\/><\\/font><\\/b><\\/div><div><div style=\\\"text-align:justify;\\\"><font color=\\\"#000000\\\" face=\\\"helvetica\\\" size=\\\"4\\\">Welcome to Multitech. We are committed to protecting your privacy and ensuring that your personal\\u00a0information is handled in a safe and responsible manner. This Privacy Policy outlines how we collect, use,\\u00a0disclose, and safeguard your information when you visit our website or make a\\u00a0purchase from us.\\u00a0Please read this Privacy Policy carefully. By accessing or using our site, you agree to the terms of this\\u00a0Privacy Policy.<\\/font><\\/div><div style=\\\"text-align:justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:1rem;\\\"><font color=\\\"#000000\\\" face=\\\"helvetica\\\"><br \\/><\\/font><\\/span><\\/div><h2 style=\\\"text-align:justify;\\\"><b><font color=\\\"#000000\\\" face=\\\"helvetica\\\">Information We Collect<\\/font><\\/b><\\/h2><div style=\\\"text-align:justify;\\\"><font color=\\\"#000000\\\" face=\\\"helvetica\\\"><br \\/><\\/font><\\/div><div style=\\\"text-align:justify;\\\"><font color=\\\"#000000\\\" face=\\\"helvetica\\\" size=\\\"4\\\">We collect various types of information when you interact with our website, including:<\\/font><\\/div><div style=\\\"text-align:justify;\\\"><font color=\\\"#000000\\\" face=\\\"helvetica\\\" size=\\\"4\\\"><br \\/><\\/font><\\/div><div style=\\\"text-align:justify;\\\"><font color=\\\"#000000\\\" face=\\\"helvetica\\\" size=\\\"4\\\">a. Personal Information\\u00a0<\\/font><\\/div><div style=\\\"text-align:justify;\\\"><font color=\\\"#000000\\\" face=\\\"helvetica\\\" size=\\\"4\\\"><br \\/><\\/font><\\/div><div style=\\\"text-align:justify;\\\"><font color=\\\"#000000\\\" face=\\\"helvetica\\\" size=\\\"4\\\">When you register on our site, place an order, or contact us, we may collect:\\u00a0<\\/font><\\/div><div><ol><li style=\\\"text-align:justify;\\\"><font color=\\\"#000000\\\" face=\\\"helvetica\\\" size=\\\"4\\\">Full Name\\u00a0<\\/font><\\/li><li style=\\\"text-align:justify;\\\"><font color=\\\"#000000\\\" face=\\\"helvetica\\\" size=\\\"4\\\">Email Address\\u00a0<\\/font><\\/li><li style=\\\"text-align:justify;\\\"><font color=\\\"#000000\\\" face=\\\"helvetica\\\" size=\\\"4\\\">Phone Number\\u00a0<\\/font><\\/li><li style=\\\"text-align:justify;\\\"><font color=\\\"#000000\\\" face=\\\"helvetica\\\" size=\\\"4\\\">Billing and Shipping Address\\u00a0<\\/font><\\/li><li style=\\\"text-align:justify;\\\"><font color=\\\"#000000\\\" face=\\\"helvetica\\\" size=\\\"4\\\">Payment Information (processed securely via third-party payment gateways)\\u00a0<\\/font><\\/li><li style=\\\"text-align:justify;\\\"><font color=\\\"#000000\\\" face=\\\"helvetica\\\" size=\\\"4\\\">Account credentials (if you create an account)<\\/font><\\/li><\\/ol><\\/div><div style=\\\"text-align:justify;\\\"><font color=\\\"#000000\\\" face=\\\"helvetica\\\" size=\\\"4\\\"><br \\/><\\/font><\\/div><div style=\\\"text-align:justify;\\\"><font color=\\\"#000000\\\" face=\\\"helvetica\\\" size=\\\"4\\\">b. Non-Personal Information\\u00a0<\\/font><\\/div><div style=\\\"text-align:justify;\\\"><font color=\\\"#000000\\\" face=\\\"helvetica\\\" size=\\\"4\\\"><br \\/><\\/font><\\/div><div style=\\\"text-align:justify;\\\"><font color=\\\"#000000\\\" face=\\\"helvetica\\\" size=\\\"4\\\">Automatically collected through cookies and other tracking technologies:\\u00a0<\\/font><\\/div><div><ol><li style=\\\"text-align:justify;\\\"><font color=\\\"#000000\\\" face=\\\"helvetica\\\" size=\\\"4\\\">IP address\\u00a0<\\/font><\\/li><li style=\\\"text-align:justify;\\\"><font color=\\\"#000000\\\" face=\\\"helvetica\\\" size=\\\"4\\\">Browser type and version\\u00a0<\\/font><\\/li><li style=\\\"text-align:justify;\\\"><font color=\\\"#000000\\\" face=\\\"helvetica\\\" size=\\\"4\\\">Device type and operating system\\u00a0<\\/font><\\/li><li style=\\\"text-align:justify;\\\"><font color=\\\"#000000\\\" face=\\\"helvetica\\\" size=\\\"4\\\">Pages visited and time spent on the site\\u00a0<\\/font><\\/li><li style=\\\"text-align:justify;\\\"><font color=\\\"#000000\\\" face=\\\"helvetica\\\" size=\\\"4\\\">Referring URLs\\u00a0<\\/font><\\/li><\\/ol><div style=\\\"text-align:justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:14px;\\\"><font color=\\\"#000000\\\" face=\\\"helvetica\\\"><br \\/><\\/font><\\/span><\\/div><\\/div><h2 style=\\\"text-align:justify;\\\"><b><font color=\\\"#000000\\\" face=\\\"helvetica\\\">How We Use Your Information<\\/font><\\/b><\\/h2><div style=\\\"text-align:justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:1rem;\\\"><font color=\\\"#000000\\\" face=\\\"helvetica\\\"><br \\/><\\/font><\\/span><\\/div><div style=\\\"text-align:justify;\\\"><font color=\\\"#000000\\\" face=\\\"helvetica\\\" size=\\\"4\\\">We use the information we collect to:\\u00a0<\\/font><\\/div><div><ol><li style=\\\"text-align:justify;\\\"><font color=\\\"#000000\\\" face=\\\"helvetica\\\" size=\\\"4\\\">Process and fulfill your orders\\u00a0<\\/font><\\/li><li style=\\\"text-align:justify;\\\"><font color=\\\"#000000\\\" face=\\\"helvetica\\\" size=\\\"4\\\">Provide customer service and support\\u00a0<\\/font><\\/li><li style=\\\"text-align:justify;\\\"><font color=\\\"#000000\\\" face=\\\"helvetica\\\" size=\\\"4\\\">Improve our website, products, and services\\u00a0<\\/font><\\/li><li style=\\\"text-align:justify;\\\"><font color=\\\"#000000\\\" face=\\\"helvetica\\\" size=\\\"4\\\">Send you order updates and transactional communications\\u00a0<\\/font><\\/li><li style=\\\"text-align:justify;\\\"><font color=\\\"#000000\\\" face=\\\"helvetica\\\" size=\\\"4\\\">Send marketing emails or promotions (you can opt out at any time)\\u00a0<\\/font><\\/li><li style=\\\"text-align:justify;\\\"><font color=\\\"#000000\\\" face=\\\"helvetica\\\" size=\\\"4\\\">Detect and prevent fraud or other unauthorized activities\\u00a0<\\/font><\\/li><li style=\\\"text-align:justify;\\\"><font color=\\\"#000000\\\" face=\\\"helvetica\\\" size=\\\"4\\\">Comply with legal obligations<\\/font><\\/li><\\/ol><div style=\\\"text-align:justify;\\\"><font color=\\\"#000000\\\" face=\\\"helvetica\\\"><br \\/><\\/font><\\/div><\\/div><h2 style=\\\"text-align:justify;\\\"><b><font color=\\\"#000000\\\" face=\\\"helvetica\\\">How We Share Your Information<\\/font><\\/b><\\/h2><div style=\\\"text-align:justify;\\\"><b><font color=\\\"#000000\\\" face=\\\"helvetica\\\"><br \\/><\\/font><\\/b><\\/div><div style=\\\"text-align:justify;\\\"><font color=\\\"#000000\\\" face=\\\"helvetica\\\" size=\\\"4\\\">We do not sell your personal data. We may share your information with third parties in the following\\u00a0situations:\\u00a0<\\/font><\\/div><div style=\\\"text-align:justify;\\\"><font color=\\\"#000000\\\" face=\\\"helvetica\\\" size=\\\"4\\\"><b>Service Providers:<\\/b> For payment processing, shipping, analytics, and marketing services.\\u00a0<\\/font><\\/div><div style=\\\"text-align:justify;\\\"><font color=\\\"#000000\\\" face=\\\"helvetica\\\" size=\\\"4\\\"><b>Business Transfers:<\\/b> In the event of a merger, sale, or acquisition of our business.\\u00a0<\\/font><\\/div><div style=\\\"text-align:justify;\\\"><font color=\\\"#000000\\\" face=\\\"helvetica\\\" size=\\\"4\\\"><b>Legal Requirements:<\\/b> When required by law or to protect our rights and users\' safety.\\u00a0<\\/font><\\/div><div style=\\\"text-align:justify;\\\"><font color=\\\"#000000\\\" face=\\\"helvetica\\\" size=\\\"4\\\"><b>Third-Party Integrations: <\\/b>Such as analytics providers (Google Analytics),