000000\\\" face=\\\"helvetica\\\"><\\/font><h4><b><font color=\\\"#000000\\\" face=\\\"helvetica\\\">Orders and Payments<\\/font><\\/b><\\/h4><div><b><font color=\\\"#000000\\\" face=\\\"helvetica\\\" size=\\\"4\\\"><br \\/><\\/font><\\/b><\\/div><div><font size=\\\"4\\\" color=\\\"#000000\\\"><font face=\\\"helvetica\\\">By placing an order, you agree to provide accurate payment and shipping information. Product prices or\\u00a0<\\/font><span style=\\\"font-family:helvetica;\\\">stock availability may change at any time without prior notice. We reserve the right to cancel or reject\\u00a0<\\/span><span style=\\\"font-family:helvetica;\\\">any order due to stock, pricing, or other reasons. Online payments are securely processed through\\u00a0<\\/span><span style=\\\"font-family:helvetica;\\\">trusted third-party payment gateways. We do not store your payment card information.<\\/span><\\/font><\\/div><div><font color=\\\"#000000\\\" face=\\\"helvetica\\\"><br \\/><\\/font><\\/div><h4><b><font color=\\\"#000000\\\" face=\\\"helvetica\\\">Shipping and Delivery<\\/font><\\/b><\\/h4><div><b><font color=\\\"#000000\\\" face=\\\"helvetica\\\"><br \\/><\\/font><\\/b><\\/div><div><font size=\\\"4\\\" color=\\\"#000000\\\"><font face=\\\"helvetica\\\">If the product you ordered is in our stock and your payment has been completed, your order will be\\u00a0<\\/font><span style=\\\"font-family:helvetica;\\\">processed within 48-72 hours. We strive to deliver products on time; however, Multitech is not\\u00a0<\\/span><span style=\\\"font-family:helvetica;\\\">responsible for any delays caused by the courier service provider or unexpected events during transit.\\u00a0<\\/span><span style=\\\"font-family:helvetica;\\\">Ownership and risk transfer to you as soon as the product is handed over to the shipping provider.\\u00a0<\\/span><span style=\\\"font-family:helvetica;\\\">Multitech reserves the right to cancel your order at any time without prior notice.<\\/span><\\/font><\\/div>