\\\"><br \\/><\\/font><\\/div><div><ol><li style=\\\"text-align:justify;\\\"><font color=\\\"#000000\\\" size=\\\"4\\\">The product is not compatible with my device (Product Specifications are clearly mentioned on the site).<\\/font><\\/li><li style=\\\"text-align:justify;\\\"><font color=\\\"#000000\\\" size=\\\"4\\\">I accidentally ordered the product.<\\/font><\\/li><li style=\\\"text-align:justify;\\\"><font color=\\\"#000000\\\" size=\\\"4\\\"><a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/multitech.com.bd\\/policy\\/terms\\\" title=\\\"\\\">The product does not look as I expected.<\\/a><\\/font><\\/li><\\/ol><div><font color=\\\"#000000\\\"><br \\/><\\/font><\\/div><\\/div><h4><b><font color=\\\"#000000\\\">Refund Policy<\\/font><\\/b><\\/h4><div><b><font color=\\\"#000000\\\"><br \\/><\\/font><\\/b><\\/div><div><ol><li style=\\\"text-align:justify;\\\"><font color=\\\"#000000\\\" size=\\\"4\\\">If a refund is approved for a valid reason, it may take 3-7 working days to be processed. For online payments, it may take longer.<\\/font><\\/li><li style=\\\"text-align:justify;\\\"><font color=\\\"#000000\\\" size=\\\"4\\\">If any cashback offer was used during the purchase, the cashback amount will be deducted from the refund.<\\/font><\\/li><li style=\\\"text-align:justify;\\\"><font color=\\\"#000000\\\" size=\\\"4\\\">For payments made via the mobile banking services, the online gateways, or POS payment, a refund charge will apply.<\\/font><\\/li><li style=\\\"text-align:justify;\\\"><font color=\\\"#000000\\\" size=\\\"4\\\">If you return a product via courier and apply for a refund, our authority will not be held responsible for any damaged or burnt items received. In such cases, the responsibility will lie with the customer, and the item will be considered ineligible for a refund.<\\/font><\\/li><li style=\\\"text-align:justify;\\\"><font color=\\\"#000000\\\" size=\\\"4\\\">No complaints will be accepted later regarding such damaged products.<\\/font><\\/li><\\/ol><div style=\\\"t