(73, 'basic', '', 'text_content.element', '{\"title\":\"Best CCTV Camera Shop in Bangladesh\",\"description\":\"<p style=\\\"text-align:justify;\\\">Looking for the <span>best CCTV camera shop in Bangladesh<\\/span>? Look no further! At <span>Multitech<\\/span>, we offer the most reliable, affordable, and high-quality CCTV camera solutions for your home, office, or business. Whether you need a complete surveillance system or a single camera setup, Multitech has got you covered.<\\/p><p style=\\\"text-align:justify;\\\">With years of experience in the security industry, Multitech has become a trusted name for CCTV cameras and accessories in Bangladesh. We stock a wide range of top brands, including Hikvision, Dahua, Uniview, CP Plus, and more. Our cameras come in various types \\u2013 from HD analog to IP cameras, wireless to PTZ \\u2013 all designed to give you peace of mind with crystal-clear video quality and 24\\/7 monitoring.<\\/p><p style=\\\"text-align:justify;\\\">What sets us apart as the <span>best CCTV camera shop in Bangladesh<\\/span> is not just our product variety, but also our unbeatable customer service. We provide expert consultation, fast delivery, and professional installation support all over the country. Our knowledgeable team helps you choose the right CCTV camera based on your budget and needs, ensuring maximum security without overspending.<\\/p><p>\\n\\n\\n<\\/p><p style=\\\"text-align:justify;\\\">At Multitech, we also offer the best prices in the market, with regular deals and discounts available online. Our easy-to-navigate e-commerce platform allows you to browse, compare, and order your CCTV products from anywhere in Bangladesh with just a few clicks.<\\/p>\"}', NULL, '2025-07-01 16:39:46', '2025-07-16 18:02:36'),
(74, 'basic', '', 'text_content.element', '{\"title\":\"Best Networking Product Supplier in Bangladesh\",\"description\":\"<p style=\\\"text-align:justify;\\\">Looking for the <span>best networking product supplier in Bangladesh<\\/span>? A good supplier can make a big difference when it comes to internet speed, smooth connection, and stable network setup. Whether you are setting up a small office, a large company, or a home network, choosing the right networking products is very important.<\\/p><p style=\\\"text-align:justify;\\\">In Bangladesh, many people face issues like poor signal, low coverage, or slow speed. These problems often happen due to low-quality or fake products. That\\u2019s why it\\u2019s important to buy from a trusted supplier who offers original and high-performance networking devices.<\\/p><p style=\\\"text-align:justify;\\\">A reliable networking product supplier always provides genuine products from popular brands like TP-Link, MikroTik, Cisco, D-Link, Tenda, Netgear, and more. You can find everything from routers, switches, access points, range extenders, network cables, PoE switches, and CCTV networking solutions. The supplier also helps you understand which product fits your needs, whether for gaming, office, ISP, or CCTV systems.<\\/p><p style=\\\"text-align:justify;\\\">Many good suppliers in Bangladesh now work fully online. You don\\u2019t need to visit a shop. You can check their products, compare models, see prices, and place orders from your home. A good online supplier also offers fast delivery and helpful support.<\\/p><p style=\\\"text-align:justify;\\\">When choosing the <span>best networking product supplier in Bangladesh<\\/span>, always check product quality, brand, price, warranty, and customer reviews. A trusted supplier will give you clear product information and help you with any issue, even after purchase.<\\/p><p style=\\\"text-align:justify;\\\">If you want smooth internet, secure networking, and long-lasting performance, always buy from a reliable source. It will save you time, money, and future problems.<\\/p><p style=\\\"text-align:justify;\\\">\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n<\\/p><p style=\\\"text-align:justify;\\\">So, whether you need a router for your home, a switch for your office, or full networking equipment for business, choose the best online networking product supplier in Bangladesh and enjoy hassle-free service with original products.<\\/p>\"}', NULL, '2025-07-15 11:45:18', '2025-07-20 12:47:30'),
