(10, 5, 'Hivideo H4A 4-Lens Smart Outdoor Wifi Camera', 'hivideo-h4a-4-lens-smart-outdoor-wifi-camera', NULL, '<div style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); font-size: 14px; text-align: justify;\"><font size=\"4\" face=\"trebuchet ms\">The Hivideo H4A Outdoor WiFi Camera is designed to bring reliable security and peace of mind to your home or business. Built with modern technology and a durable design, this camera is made for outdoor use where both performance and protection matter the most. With its strong build quality and weather-resistant design, it can easily withstand rain, dust, and other outdoor conditions, ensuring continuous monitoring all year round.</font></div><div style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); font-size: 14px; text-align: justify;\"><font size=\"4\" face=\"trebuchet ms\"><br></font></div><div style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); font-size: 14px; text-align: justify;\"><font size=\"4\" face=\"trebuchet ms\">One of the biggest advantages of the Hivideo H4A is its wireless connectivity. Instead of dealing with complicated cabling, this camera connects directly to your WiFi network, making installation simple and flexible. Whether you want to mount it near your front door, in the backyard, or at your office entrance, it can be placed in the most suitable position without the hassle of long wires. The wireless feature also makes it easy to adjust or move the camera whenever your security needs change.</font></div><div style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); font-size: 14px; text-align: justify;\"><font size=\"4\" face=\"trebuchet ms\"><br></font></div><div style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); font-size: 14px; text-align: justify;\"><font size=\"4\" face=\"trebuchet ms\">The H4A Outdoor WiFi Camera is designed to deliver clear and detailed video footage. This ensures that you can monitor every activity around your property with confidence. From daytime monitoring to night surveillance, the camera provides consistent results, making it a dependable choice for 24/7 security. With its 