(22, 6, 'Original WGP mini UPS 5/9/12V, 10400mAh Lithium Battery', 'original-wgp-mini-ups-5912v-10400mah-lithium-battery', NULL, '<div><b>New WGP Mini UPS – Router &amp; ONU Backup Up to 8 Hours (5V, 9V, 12V Output) – 10400mAh | Price in Bangladesh</b></div><div><br></div><div>The New WGP Mini UPS with a 10400mAh (38.48Wh) capacity is a reliable backup power solution designed for routers, ONU devices, CCTV cameras, and other low-voltage equipment. With support for 5V, 9V, and 12V outputs, this compact UPS ensures uninterrupted internet connectivity during load shedding and protects your devices from sudden power spikes and thunder-related voltage surges.</div><div><br></div><div><b>Specifications</b></div><div><br></div><div>Battery Capacity: 10400mAh (38.48Wh)</div><div>Type: Multi-output mini UPS</div><div>Battery Life Cycle: Approx. 500 cycles</div><div>Input: 12V-2A</div><div>Outputs:</div><div>• 5V-1A</div><div>• 9V-1A</div><div>• 12V-1A</div><div>Working Temperature: –20°C to 65°C</div><div>UPS Input Jack: 5.5 × 2.1 mm</div><div>USB Output: 5V USB</div><div>DC Cable: 5.5 × 2.5 mm</div><div><br></div><div><b>Package Contents</b></div><div><br></div><div>• 1 × User Manual</div><div>• 2 × DC-to-DC Cables</div><div><br></div><div><b>Product Overview</b></div><div><br></div><div>The WGP Mini UPS provides 7–8 hours of backup for routers, ONU devices, or CCTV cameras depending on the power consumption of each device. Even during complete power outages, you can continue using broadband internet without interruption. Its multi-voltage output makes it compatible with a wide range of electronics that run on 5V, 9V, or 12V.</div><div><br></div><div>This small yet powerful UPS is ideal for homes, offices, and especially rural areas where load shedding occurs frequently. In addition to backup power, it also safeguards your network equipment from harmful surge voltages caused by thunderstorms.</div><div><br></div><div><b>Protection from Thunder &amp; Surge</b></div><div><b><